Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:14.38,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感情の名前なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:18.39,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}言い出せばキリがないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:22.00,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君の目が叫ぶのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.20,0:22:26.06,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本能で聞き分ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:26.65,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trust
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:27.91,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}付き纏う
